high_descs: Turn around and walk to the glass coffee table.
Pick up the gold bottle on the coffee table.
Turn to your right and walk to the desk.
Place the bottle on the desk on the coffee table.
Turn around and walk to the coffee table again.
Pick up the white bottle on the coffee table.
Walk back to the desk.
Place the white bottle next to the gold bottle on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a white and a gold bottle on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and go through the doorway into the living room.  Move toward the glass coffee table.
Grab the gold vase off of the coffee table.
Move right, then left, then forward, then right again and move towards the black desk.
Place the gold vase onto to the black desk.
Move right, then left, then right again and move towards the glass coffee table.
Pick up the white vase off of the coffee table.
Move right, then left, then forward, then right again and move towards the black desk.
Place the white vase onto the black desk.
anns.task_desc: Move both vases from the coffee table to the desk.

high_descs: turn around to the left and walk through the doorway to the glass coffee table
pick up the yellow vase on the left
go to the desk to your left
place the vase on the desk directly opposite of the desk chair
turn around and go to the glass coffee table
pick up the white vase on the coffee table
go to the desk on your left
place white vase to the left next to yellow vase
anns.task_desc: Move a two vases from the coffee table to the desk

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the wall, take a right at the table, cross the room, hang a left at the glass table, take a right at the couch and turn left to face the glass table.
Pick up the orange bottle from the left corner of the table.
Turn right, take a left at the chair and walk to the black desk on your right.
Put the orange bottle on the desk in the middle near the edge.
Turn right, take a right at the chair, turn left at the table, take a right at the couch and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the white bottle from the left side of the table.
Turn right, take a left at the chair and walk to the black desk on your right.
Put the white bottle to the left of the orange bottle on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles on a desk.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the wall then turn left and walk until you are lined up with the glass coffee table in the living room and go to it.
Pick up the yellow bottle on the bottom left corner of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk to the chair then turn left and walk forward until you are lined up with the black desk then walk to the black desk.
Put the yellow bottle near the edge of the black table slightly to the right of the center.
Go back to where you got the first bottle.
Pick up the frosted glass bottle near the edge of the coffee table.
Walk back over to the desk where you put the yellow bottle.
Place the frosted bottle to the left of the yellow bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place two glass bottles on the desk in the living room.
